These docs are available in HTML format form:

http://www.pagekit.org/guide

To compile the source into HTML, download Saxon, J2DK 1.3, and Norman
Walsh's DocBook XSL stylesheets from:

http://www.nwalsh.com/docbook/xsl/

Then run

java -cp /home/tjmather/saxon com.icl.saxon.StyleSheet ../docsrc/manual.xml ../../docbook_xsl/html/chunk.xsl > index.html
